Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.75,00:00:11.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,This will probably be my will.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.29,00:00:18.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Things have calmed down a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.79,00:00:21.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I can't say I'm happy with how things turned out,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.45,00:00:26.12,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,but I've got a little bit of time, \Nso I figured it was a good time to write this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.04,00:00:29.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,My name is Megumi Sakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.45,00:00:34.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I was a Japanese teacher at Megurigaoka High.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.79,00:00:43.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No... I still am...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.20,00:00:50.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,...even if this school is not the same place it was before.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.75,00:00:59.12,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,The first time I realized it was when \NI stood on the roof on that fateful day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.45,00:01:04.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No, it was earlier than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.16,00:01:11.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'd felt the signs that it was coming some time before.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.04,00:01:15.00,Caption,,0,0,0,,School Living Club
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.66,00:01:18.33,Caption,,0,0,0,,Cause you wanna do it, if you wanna do it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.33,00:01:20.20,Caption,,0,0,0,,When you wanna do it, you wanna do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.20,00:01:21.54,Caption,,0,0,0,,Let's do it together! (Yeah!)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.66,00:01:24.54,Caption,,0,0,0,,We are right here
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.70,00:01:27.91,Caption,,0,0,0,,We have dreams here, too
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.08,00:01:31.04,Caption,,0,0,0,,If you're talking about buddies,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.08,00:01:31.04,Caption2,,0,0,0,,you're talking about your friends! (That's right!)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.04,00:01:34.20,Caption,,0,0,0,,I tried saying "I love you!" (I love you so much!)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.75,00:01:51.04,Caption,,0,0,0,,You know what you have to do after school
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.04,00:01:52.37,Caption,,0,0,0,,Come on, now, get together!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.37,00:01:54.20,Caption,,0,0,0,,Don't sneak off to go home! (Hey!)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.20,00:01:57.37,Caption,,0,0,0,,How about club? Let's get something done!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.50,00:01:59.91,Caption,,0,0,0,,Don't go playing around!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.91,00:02:03.79,Caption,,0,0,0,,That girl says "I'm back" (Welcome back!)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.79,00:02:06.95,Caption,,0,0,0,,We'll be fine as long as we're together (Club!)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.95,00:02:10.20,Caption,,0,0,0,,Everybody say: let's all be friends
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.20,00:02:11.75,Caption,,0,0,0,,Cause you wanna do it, if you wanna do it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.75,00:02:13.66,Caption,,0,0,0,,when you wanna do it, you wanna do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.66,00:02:15.00,Caption,,0,0,0,,I love you so much! (Yeah!)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.00,00:02:18.12,Caption,,0,0,0,,We are enjoying our lives
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.12,00:02:21.16,Caption,,0,0,0,,We're having fun 24 hours a day
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.62,00:02:24.58,Caption,,0,0,0,,The red sun shines bright on the roof
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.58,00:02:28.00,Caption,,0,0,0,,I tried shouting out to it (We're doing great!)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.00,00:02:31.04,Caption,,0,0,0,,We are right here
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.04,00:02:34.33,Caption,,0,0,0,,We have dreams here, too
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.62,00:02:37.70,Caption,,0,0,0,,If you're talking about buddies,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.62,00:02:37.70,Caption2,,0,0,0,,you're talking about your friends! (That's right!)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.70,00:02:40.83,Caption,,0,0,0,,I tried saying "I love you!" (I love you so much!)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.08,00:02:43.62,Caption,,0,0,0,,I love
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.08,00:02:43.62,Caption2,,0,0,0,,Megu-nee
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.62,00:02:47.00,Caption,,0,0,0,,I love
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.62,00:02:47.00,Caption2,,0,0,0,,Megu-nee
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.62,00:02:47.00,Caption3,,0,0,0,,Back Then
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.66,00:03:14.91,Caption,,0,0,0,,Message Inbox
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.66,00:03:14.91,Caption2,,0,0,0,,From: Mom
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.66,00:03:14.91,Caption3,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.66,00:03:14.91,Caption4,,0,0,0,,From: Mom
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.67,00:03:14.91,Caption5,,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.67,00:03:14.91,Caption6,,0,0,0,,From: Mom
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.67,00:03:14.91,Caption7,,0,0,0,,Take care of yourself, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.37,00:03:21.66,Caption,,0,0,0,,Sender: Mom
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.37,00:03:21.66,Caption2,,0,0,0,,To: Megumi
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.37,00:03:21.66,Caption3,,0,0,0,,Subj: Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.37,00:03:21.66,Caption4,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Megumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.37,00:03:21.66,Caption5,,0,0,0,,Are you doing a good job as a teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.38,00:03:21.66,Caption6,,0,0,0,,I'm a little worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.38,00:03:21.66,Caption7,,0,0,0,,You were always quiet as a child,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.38,00:03:21.66,Caption8,,0,0,0,,not that that's a bad thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.38,00:03:21.66,Caption9,,0,0,0,,but taking care of your students
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.54,00:03:42.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Ribbon, ribbon...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.12,00:03:58.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.79,00:04:12.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Mom again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.83,00:04:14.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm driving!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.37,00:04:17.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I know you're worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.95,00:04:22.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I know you said I wasn't suited to be a teacher, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.04,00:04:27.37,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,You said it when I started my education track, \Nand when I got my teaching license.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.54,00:04:31.16,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,I wonder what's going on? \NThere are so many sirens this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.33,00:04:36.50,Caption,,0,0,0,,Teacher's Office
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.33,00:04:36.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't say you're not suited to be a teacher,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.75,00:04:41.20,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,but you must maintain distance \Nbetween you and your students.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.58,00:04:46.20,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Saying you're on friendly terms \Nwith students may sound nice,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.66,00:04:47.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,but teachers are not on the same level as students.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.12,00:04:49.79,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,I'm not suited to be a teacher, huh... \Nbut teachers are not on the same level as students.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.79,00:04:50.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,but teachers are not on the same level as students.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.08,00:04:52.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.29,00:04:54.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.00,00:05:00.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.04,00:05:04.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The vice principal says that to all the young teachers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.00,00:05:05.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.50,00:05:08.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We're going to cut to a camera on the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.00,00:05:10.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,An alarming amount of accidents have occurred.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.25,00:05:11.87,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,What's going on? \NAn alarming amount of accidents have occurred.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.87,00:05:13.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,An alarming amount of accidents have occurred.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.20,00:05:13.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,While the reason behind them is still unknown,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.58,00:05:15.00,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,That's crazy. \NWhile the reason behind them is still unknown,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.20,00:05:16.75,Caption,,0,0,0,,Dozens of car accidents reported in Megurigaoka
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.00,00:05:16.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,citizens are hoping for a swift response to prevent more.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.41,00:05:26.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Alright, I'm going to pass back last week's tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.08,00:05:28.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Ishizuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.29,00:05:29.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.58,00:05:30.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Shoujouji.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.83,00:05:31.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.04,00:05:33.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Sera.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.04,00:05:33.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.20,00:05:35.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Takeya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.87,00:05:38.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yuki Takeya?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.20,00:05:40.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.83,00:05:43.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Look at her hat...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.25,00:05:45.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'd like you to retake it after class.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.16,00:05:49.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You're so mean, Megu-nee.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.08,00:05:52.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Don't call me Megu-nee. It's Sakura-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.75,00:05:57.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,On friendly terms with the students...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.16,00:06:00.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Is that what this is?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.20,00:06:05.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Bye, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.08,00:06:06.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.87,00:06:08.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Man, I feel bad for Megu-nee.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.41,00:06:13.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.12,00:06:16.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Is it hard to concentrate with me right next to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.95,00:06:21.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I don't like tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.54,00:06:26.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But I don't dislike being with you, Megu-nee.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.25,00:06:31.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Then let's try our best, together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.66,00:06:54.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yuki-chan, I'm going to step out for just a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.45,00:06:58.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'll be right in the hall, so call me if you need me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.08,00:07:03.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm hungry. I wanna eat some snacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.33,00:07:05.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Once you're done with your test, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.70,00:07:15.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Ebisuzawa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.75,00:07:17.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Don't you have club right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.83,00:07:20.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.29,00:07:26.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Umm, sorry to bother you during a retake...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.62,00:07:31.79,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,But you're the only person \NI can ask for advice, Megu-nee.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.12,00:07:35.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Don't call me Megu-nee. It's Sakura-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.08,00:07:40.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I dunno, I just don't know anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.58,00:07:45.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I don't know why I'm feeling like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.41,00:07:47.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Whenever I'm with him...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.79,00:07:57.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I see, your senpai, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.66,00:07:59.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.33,00:08:02.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I think I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.87,00:08:07.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You like him and want advice, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.62,00:08:10.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wha... No, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.50,00:08:17.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Maybe, I dunno...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.20,00:08:21.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.62,00:08:24.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,maybe, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.12,00:08:28.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So there's nothing to worry about, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.16,00:08:30.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.91,00:08:34.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I feel better now that we talked.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.16,00:08:39.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I dunno why, but I can't say this stuff to anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.45,00:08:44.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But I can when I'm with you, Megu-nee.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.45,00:08:47.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Thanks for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.91,00:08:56.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'm not suited to be a teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.04,00:08:58.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.87,00:08:59.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.29,00:09:11.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You were gone so long!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.12,00:09:12.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.16,00:09:15.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I finished the test a long time ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.79,00:09:17.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.37,00:09:18.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's finally over!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.66,00:09:21.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm so tired, Megu-nee!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.04,00:09:23.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I told you, don't call me Megu-nee...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.41,00:09:29.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll get ice cream, maybe I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.75,00:09:32.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Don't buy any on your way home, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.83,00:09:35.79,Caption,,0,0,0,,Message Inbox
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.83,00:09:35.79,Caption2,,0,0,0,,From: Mom
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.83,00:09:35.79,Caption3,,0,0,0,,Emergency
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.83,00:09:35.79,Caption4,,0,0,0,,From: Mom
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.83,00:09:35.79,Caption5,,0,0,0,,Evacuate now!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.83,00:09:35.79,Caption6,,0,0,0,,From: Mom
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.83,00:09:35.79,Caption7,,0,0,0,,Please reply
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.33,00:09:39.33,Caption,,0,0,0,,...sending you this video.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.33,00:09:39.33,Caption2,,0,0,0,,...on the news
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.29,00:09:44.54,Caption,,0,0,0,,Huge traffic accidents in Megurigaoka
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.37,00:09:44.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.79,00:09:48.95,Caption,,0,0,0,,Huge traffic accidents in Megurigaoka
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.00,00:09:48.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's really close to here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.00,00:10:03.00,Caption,,0,0,0,,Chaos at Local Shopping Mall
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.00,00:10:04.83,Caption,,0,0,0,,Train lines shutting down one by one
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.00,00:10:04.83,Caption2,,0,0,0,,Suspension of service
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.83,00:10:06.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey, Megu-nee?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.91,00:10:07.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.91,00:10:10.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Megu-nee, are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.87,00:10:12.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What're you looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.58,00:10:15.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey now, don't look at other people's phones!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.58,00:10:16.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Darn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.54,00:10:18.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm going home!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.00,00:10:21.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Takeya-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.33,00:10:25.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It looks like the trains aren't running.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.08,00:10:27.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Maybe you should wait here a little while?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.08,00:10:28.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, they aren't?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.29,00:10:31.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Aww, but I'm hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.25,00:10:33.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.54,00:10:36.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Let's go up to the roof!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.37,00:10:38.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,They're growing baby tomatoes up there, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.29,00:10:40.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yes, but we can't eat those.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.83,00:10:43.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And students aren't allowed up there on their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.79,00:10:46.91,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Oh, then we can say we're \Nobserving the Gardening Club!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.91,00:10:48.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's okay then, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.70,00:10:51.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.70,00:10:59.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The door's unlocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.62,00:11:01.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.12,00:11:04.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I forgot to lock it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.70,00:11:07.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Could you please lock it for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.37,00:11:11.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.87,00:11:15.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, are you in the Gardening Club?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.00,00:11:17.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,As you can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.00,00:11:19.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Are you here to observe?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.08,00:11:20.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.12,00:11:22.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wow, those tomatoes look really yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.58,00:11:23.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Would you like to eat one?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.70,00:11:24.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.58,00:11:26.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Sure, if you're going to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.95,00:11:27.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.37,00:11:40.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yuri-san, do you always do all this work alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.75,00:11:41.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.87,00:11:44.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,For some reason, nobody else came today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.83,00:11:48.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Why isn't Mom picking up?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.87,00:11:49.87,Caption,,0,0,0,,Call Ended
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.87,00:11:49.87,Caption2,,0,0,0,,Home
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.87,00:11:51.87,Caption,,0,0,0,,Incoming Call
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.87,00:11:51.87,Caption2,,0,0,0,,Kamiyama-sensei
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.00,00:11:55.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hel-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.00,00:11:57.87,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?! \NSakura-san, where are you right now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.62,00:12:01.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.95,00:12:04.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Maybe another club member who's on duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.04,00:12:07.83,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,The roof? Lock the door, \Nand don't let anyone up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.83,00:12:08.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The teacher's office is al-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.83,00:12:19.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wait a sec, I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.50,00:12:20.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.91,00:12:25.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Megu-nee?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.04,00:12:29.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I have to open the door for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.45,00:12:31.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.95,00:12:39.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Please, open the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.37,00:12:44.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Ebisuzawa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.00,00:12:48.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hurry, lock it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.16,00:12:51.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,He's hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.25,00:12:53.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.50,00:12:55.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Sensei, we have to get him to the infirmary!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.70,00:12:57.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You can't go down there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.50,00:12:59.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You can't anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.58,00:13:01.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.50,00:13:17.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Everyone just...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.04,00:13:23.66,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Turned into those things, \Nand then the Track Club was surrounded...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.16,00:13:25.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Then, Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.12,00:13:27.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Senpai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.29,00:13:30.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We have to go out and call an ambulance!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.20,00:13:33.70,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,No, I've been calling for one, \Nbut my phone won't connect!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.25,00:13:45.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I don't get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.75,00:13:48.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.12,00:13:51.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Why is this happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.08,00:14:05.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Dammit, they're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.83,00:14:11.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We can use the Gardening Club's locker!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.16,00:14:24.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wakasa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.12,00:14:29.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Takeya-san, push the washing machine over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.08,00:14:38.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Senpai...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.66,00:14:44.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Ebisuzawa-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.70,00:14:56.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Ebisuzawa-san, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.66,00:15:49.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You dummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.08,00:15:52.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Why are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.00,00:16:00.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And what's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.20,00:16:02.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wearing that weird hat...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.33,00:16:07.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Sensei, what should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.62,00:16:11.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,With school, and outside as it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.50,00:16:13.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.16,00:16:15.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.45,00:16:29.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,A lot of people lost their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.33,00:16:33.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Students and teachers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.20,00:16:38.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Those girls are the only ones left here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.87,00:16:43.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I believe someone will come to save us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.41,00:16:47.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,As long as I'm alive, I'll protect them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.37,00:16:50.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,After all,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.12,00:16:51.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm their teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.41,00:16:57.41,Caption,,0,0,0,,School Living Club
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.50,00:17:00.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.83,00:17:07.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's so dry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.70,00:17:13.91,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,I can't say I dislike hardtack, \Nbut it's hard eating it for a meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.33,00:17:15.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.54,00:17:19.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The power's out at school today, so we can't cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.95,00:17:23.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But I like blackouts!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.75,00:17:25.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,They're kinda exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.16,00:17:28.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Our water heater's electric, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.45,00:17:29.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.08,00:17:30.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So we don't have any hot water.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.54,00:17:34.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Nooo, my bath...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.37,00:17:36.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.37,00:17:39.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I hope it rains.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.75,00:17:40.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.83,00:17:42.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Then I could take a shower!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.91,00:17:44.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What are you, a dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.41,00:17:45.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.41,00:17:46.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Not even Taromaru would do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.95,00:17:51.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Let's go camping!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.66,00:17:54.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.79,00:17:56.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I said camping!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.41,00:17:58.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Camping?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.70,00:18:02.58,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,C'mon, you know other clubs have \Nfield trips and go camping, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.58,00:18:06.45,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Well, we're the School Living Club, \Nso we should camp out at school!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.45,00:18:08.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, that sounds great!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.08,00:18:11.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You're going to pitch a tent in the classroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.33,00:18:14.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I get it, there's no electricity when you're camping.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.66,00:18:17.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We should have a tent in our room.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.00,00:18:19.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It should fit four people.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.08,00:18:22.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Then it'll fit all of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.70,00:18:24.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey, what about me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.45,00:18:28.87,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,I-it's okay, we can fit you in \Nif we squish together, Megu-nee!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.08,00:18:31.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I didn't mean to...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.75,00:18:33.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry, Megu-nee.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.00,00:18:37.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No, I'm kidding. We need a lookout, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.83,00:18:39.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.37,00:18:42.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Megu-nee...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.45,00:18:45.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,thanks for working so hard all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.08,00:18:48.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What's this, all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.70,00:18:50.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.70,00:18:53.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah, thanks, Megu-nee.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.00,00:18:54.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Good, uh, work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.37,00:19:02.66,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Goodness, don't call me Megu-nee. \NIt's Sakura-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.04,00:19:04.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.37,00:19:15.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It really feels like camping!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.37,00:19:19.04,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,You're right. Now's the time when \Nwe tell scary stories, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.66,00:19:21.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It feels like camping, sure, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.79,00:19:23.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.04,00:19:27.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Did you know that on a dark night like tonight...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.04,00:19:29.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Chop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.37,00:19:31.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Owie!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.50,00:19:36.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Do you have any stories that aren't scary?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.25,00:19:38.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.16,00:19:39.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.41,00:19:42.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You've gotta have something!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.33,00:19:44.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,C'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.04,00:19:46.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Please stop touching me so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.66,00:19:49.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Aww, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.33,00:19:55.95,Caption,,0,0,0,,Pssshhh
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.54,00:19:52.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh? Mii-kun, you're bright red!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.33,00:19:54.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,C'mon, let her go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.91,00:19:59.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Ooh, then let's talk about romance!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.04,00:20:00.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Like guys we like and stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.70,00:20:06.25,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Sure, but do you even have \Nany of those stories, Yuki-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.25,00:20:07.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I sure do!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.62,00:20:09.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wait, maybe not.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.29,00:20:10.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,C'mon now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.20,00:20:13.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What about you, Kurumi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.20,00:20:14.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Ah, she avoided the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.79,00:20:17.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You love your shovel, don't you, Kurumi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.58,00:20:20.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I don't think that falls under "romance."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.00,00:20:23.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Before, when I lost my crush,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.33,00:20:25.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,you comforted me, didn't you, Yuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.91,00:20:27.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I did?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.29,00:20:30.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You're good at that, Yuki-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.70,00:20:35.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Ah, nope, I might be wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.12,00:20:37.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.12,00:20:38.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Whaaa...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.25,00:20:40.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You guys are so mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.16,00:20:44.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I hear Megu-nee!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.37,00:20:46.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Shoot, really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.58,00:20:47.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Whoa, that was fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.70,00:21:01.91,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Now, nobody's being a bad girl \Nand staying up late, are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.58,00:21:05.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's very late, so get some sleep, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.75,00:21:18.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Okay, we're good!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.29,00:21:25.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Megu-nee's keeping a lookout for us, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.62,00:21:27.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Man, that scared me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.58,00:21:29.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Were you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.79,00:21:32.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm not scared of Megu-nee!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.50,00:21:35.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Yuki-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.50,00:21:40.70,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Hey, you know, we're going to \Ngraduate sooner or later, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.70,00:21:41.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.91,00:21:47.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But Megu-nee's always going to be at our school.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.16,00:21:52.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Thinking about that makes me kinda sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.87,00:21:55.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I know how you feel. She's a great teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.66,00:21:59.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah, without her, we wouldn't be a club.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.08,00:22:01.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.45,00:22:04.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah, she's so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.37,00:22:06.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,She gives a lot of homework, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.20,00:22:08.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And sometimes her spelling's off.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.33,00:22:09.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.20,00:22:11.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But she's so nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.00,00:22:12.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Though she gives a lot of homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.75,00:22:14.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wait, we're going in circles!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.50,00:22:20.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Sensei must...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.62,00:22:25.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Megu-nee must be someone you really love.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.37,00:22:28.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yup, I love Megu-nee!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.08,00:22:40.91,Caption,,0,0,0,,Talking on our way home
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.37,00:22:45.91,Caption,,0,0,0,,Telling each other our secrets
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.54,00:22:51.37,Caption,,0,0,0,,Even when the 5-o'clock chime rings out
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.70,00:22:56.54,Caption,,0,0,0,,I wonder why I feel we still haven't talked enough
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.29,00:23:03.37,Caption,,0,0,0,,A tiny four-leaf clover
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.37,00:23:08.45,Caption,,0,0,0,,Sways in the gentle breeze
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.75,00:23:13.41,Caption,,0,0,0,,Hey, I'm sure that yes, I'm sure
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.70,00:23:20.29,Caption,,0,0,0,,I hope tomorrow will be sunny, too
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.29,00:23:25.87,Caption,,0,0,0,,We walked the road together
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.12,00:23:31.91,Caption,,0,0,0,,Always saying we'd meet at the usual place
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.41,00:23:35.83,Caption,,0,0,0,,Ah, the fluffy clouds above
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.83,00:23:41.25,Caption,,0,0,0,,Seem like they'll be burned, they're shining so bright
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.25,00:23:46.70,Caption,,0,0,0,,Even if, one day, these days
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.70,00:23:52.83,Caption,,0,0,0,,Are but a faded memory
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.08,00:23:57.91,Caption,,0,0,0,,I want to give you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.91,00:24:04.04,Caption,,0,0,0,,A lot of smiles right now
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.08,00:24:06.79,Caption,,0,0,0,,Next Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.79,00:24:11.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey Megu-nee, why did you become a teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.04,00:24:12.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, you want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.16,00:24:13.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Eh, maybe not.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.16,00:24:13.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.91,00:24:16.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,'Cause you'll always be Megu-nee!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.41,00:24:21.04,Caption,,0,0,0,,Field Trip
